64
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:27,240
You are lying.

65
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:31,150
Would you take a servant to view the lotus pond?

66
00:06:31,150 --> 00:06:34,570
Would you be concerned that your servant is not eating?

67
00:06:34,570 --> 00:06:36,240
Brother, don't forget, she is Wu Hong Da's daughter.

68
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:40,190
I'm not a three year old kid. I don't need you to tell me what to do.

69
00:06:41,820 --> 00:06:44,440
You know that I didn't say anything wrong.

70
00:06:44,440 --> 00:06:48,650
You are angry because you have a guilty conscious.

71
00:06:48,650 --> 00:06:50,700
What I said was right.

72
00:06:50,700 --> 00:06:53,900
Your feelings towards Wu Cai Hong already surpasses that of an ordinary person.

73
00:06:53,900 --> 00:06:55,920
Leave.

74
00:06:58,320 --> 00:07:00,090
