83
00:07:56,640 --> 00:08:01,900
But Miss's affections towards Master are unintentional. She lights up every time she see's him.

84
00:08:01,900 --> 00:08:05,440
No wonder Miss hates Wu Cai Hong so much.

85
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:10,580
Even though they address her as the mistress of the house, her family name is Fang not Jiang.

86
00:08:10,580 --> 00:08:13,570
She is also an outsider.

87
00:08:13,570 --> 00:08:20,930
If she can't be the Young Master's wife, she will have to marry someone and leave the house sooner or later.

88
00:08:20,930 --> 00:08:25,750
If a girl wants to marry, she should marry an authentic Young Master.

89
00:08:25,750 --> 00:08:30,330
Look. Miss has placed so many thoughts on Young Master.

90
00:08:30,330 --> 00:08:34,140
It was really rotten and a waste of time.

91
00:08:34,140 --> 00:08:36,400
