92
00:08:36,400 --> 00:08:39,380
<i>I will never leave this family.</i>

93
00:08:39,380 --> 00:08:42,530
<i>I will also never leave Mom and Brother.</i>

94
00:08:42,530 --> 00:08:47,430
<i>Wu Cai Hong. I won't let you and Brother be together.</i>

95
00:09:02,270 --> 00:09:07,570
Miss Fang. Are you really inviting me out for tea? It can't be that simple.

96
00:09:07,570 --> 00:09:10,810
