110
00:10:08,370 --> 00:10:12,730
Once a friend becomes an enemy, he becomes more dangerous than the enemy.

111
00:10:12,730 --> 00:10:17,380
Yet once an enemy becomes a friend, he will be more reliable than a friend.

112
00:10:17,380 --> 00:10:20,040
