133
00:12:03,810 --> 00:12:08,730
At the same time, I'm also here to visit my mother's foe.

134
00:12:08,730 --> 00:12:12,890
Do you still remember, three years ago, the aunt from the weaving and dyeing factory.

135
00:12:16,190 --> 00:12:19,770
Are you referring to her husband, Zhou Da Liang who had lung disease?

136
00:12:19,770 --> 00:12:23,330
I'm his son, Zhou Shao Tian.

137
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:38,680
Talking about this, you look exactly like your mother.

138
00:12:38,680 --> 00:12:43,510
Uncle Gao. I visited you without advance notice today.

139
00:12:43,510 --> 00:12:46,000
