144
00:13:06,180 --> 00:13:08,970
Why do you still want to talk about it?

145
00:13:08,970 --> 00:13:13,430
If it weren't for my mother's wish, I wouldn't want to talk about this either.

146
00:13:13,430 --> 00:13:15,180
Your mother's wish?

147
00:13:15,180 --> 00:13:17,380
When my father got sick and was lying in bed,

148
00:13:17,380 --> 00:13:19,870
Old Master Jiang took care of my mother.

149
00:13:19,870 --> 00:13:23,810
He gave her some of Ling Long's business. Old Master Jiang knew about my family's hardship.

150
00:13:23,810 --> 00:13:28,010
He gave wage advances to try to solve the urgent needs of my family.

151
00:13:28,010 --> 00:13:31,120
If it weren't for Old Master Jiang's kindness,

152
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:35,980
