155
00:13:45,910 --> 00:13:51,950
She said that someone like Old Master Jiang would never use opium to frame anyone.

156
00:13:51,950 --> 00:13:56,730
Unfortunately with our family situation the way it was, Jiang was unable to be compensated.

157
00:13:56,730 --> 00:14:00,860
Only during the Winter Solstice Festival, his burning point for money was all for nothing.

158
00:14:02,390 --> 00:14:07,760
Now with mixed effort, Old Jiang can rest in peace.

159
00:14:07,760 --> 00:14:11,160
I couldn't pay him for his kindness to my family.

160
00:14:11,160 --> 00:14:15,990
The only thing I can do is to prove Boss Jiang's innocence.

161
00:14:15,990 --> 00:14:19,410
He will then rest in peace in heaven.

162
00:14:24,550 --> 00:14:28,580
Your mother has such a son who is willing to redeem himself for the family,

163
00:14:28,580 --> 00:14:31,440
that is her good fortune.

164
00:14:32,770 --> 00:14:37,770
But the case happened twelve years ago, it won't be easy to turn around the case.

165
00:14:37,770 --> 00:14:43,390
I have no choice but to seek your help now.

166
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:48,580
I won't be able to help you

167
00:14:49,770 --> 00:14:53,910
