171
00:15:07,820 --> 00:15:14,550
The years following the wrongful death of Boss Jiang, there were a lot of people who could have cried foul.

172
00:15:14,550 --> 00:15:21,010
The strange thing is that he payed for other's grievances but everyone suffered in the end.

173
00:15:21,800 --> 00:15:27,680
I'm ashamed for not speaking sooner but now I can help prove Jiang's innocence.

174
00:15:27,680 --> 00:15:34,510
But I think when he was implicated and everyone was tight-lipped.

175
00:15:34,510 --> 00:15:40,840
I wanted to find a home for windows and orphans and find a solution

176
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:47,340
