177
00:15:47,340 --> 00:15:53,400
I sent men to find out about their whereabouts but there was no news.

178
00:15:53,400 --> 00:15:58,330
I heard that Jiang Yu is very capable now and he has gotten back Ling Long.

179
00:15:58,330 --> 00:16:04,070
At that time, I was a coward and didn't dare to speak up on his father's behalf.

180
00:16:04,070 --> 00:16:09,990
I don't have the face to see him. Thus, I have never visited him.

181
00:16:09,990 --> 00:16:15,050
