231
00:21:26,800 --> 00:21:28,240
Let me take a look.

232
00:21:28,240 --> 00:21:29,860
It's not me.

233
00:21:31,520 --> 00:21:33,600
It's Miss.

234
00:21:52,050 --> 00:21:55,980
